  "comment": {
    "text": "The \"ResponseHeaderCopied\" translation key is used to display a message when a response header is successfully copied to the clipboard in a web application. This message appears as a button label in UI elements, prompting users to perform an action on the copied data. Translators should provide a phrase that indicates success and informs the user about the action taken on the copied data.",
